{"tid":889901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訂購郭文貴T恤　惠州男尋釁滋事罪成入獄1年半","createTime":"2018-11-05T01:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T04:32:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"99a0ac26380c357b6118570f28abce0d1291fb6c","tid":889901,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181104/photo/bkn-20181104190121669-1104_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181104191341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181104190121669-1104_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181104191341&h=f3541bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東惠州男子董奇，去年訂購印上被國際刑警通緝的富商郭文貴口頭禪T恤被捕。境外傳媒報道，家屬上周四（1日）收到法院的判決書，得知董奇已被以「尋釁滋事罪」判處一年半有期徒刑，但未知他會否提出上訴。報道又指，董奇去年5月至今一直被羈押，按刑期計算，理應在本月下旬便可獲釋。 <br />\n<br />\n報道稱，警方在審訊期間明白僅憑T恤難以給董奇定罪，故在微信、QQ等平台上搜集罪證，指他曾發表討論民主、詆毀政府，以及污蔑國家領導人的言論，又指他曾轉發聲援異見人士的文章、試圖向異見人士捐款、發布「期望一人一票選舉政府」的言論，以及散布其他虛假訊息。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181104/bkn-20181104190121669-1104_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181104%2Fbkn-20181104190121669-1104_00952_001.html&d=%2Be4rXsWWmp3uQC6wDi9rWQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dfe93009\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181104/bkn-20181104190121669-1104_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d450a1b620cfcc65f222bc120c23d2561d6acd5e","tid":889901,"uid":126100,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"小支支明明話自己係民主國家，點解唔比討論民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a45e1f9d5ec99d9a26a0dbc0a618d0bd19483","tid":889901,"uid":17103,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"d450a1b620cfcc65f222bc120c23d2561d6acd5e","tid":889901,"uid":126100,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"小支支明明話自己係民主國家，點解唔比討論民主<img src=\"/a